<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateBuffer.SetManualPageSize" Title="SetManualPageSize method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateBuffer">IStateBuffer</PageRef> ->
    SetManualPageSize
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>SetManualPageSize</TypeRef> method defines a manual page size for the buffer. This can be used instead of calling BindBufferLayout.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void SetManualPageSize(size_t pageSizeInBytes);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="size_t" Name="pageSizeInBytes">
          The explicit page size, in bytes, to allocate for each state buffer page.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateBuffer">IStateBuffer</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
